		<div class="comment-body"><p>The biggest mistake people make is to be unfamiliar with the Scriptures (the Bible) and to rely on others who say they will tell them what God says.  For those who claim to speak to us on behalf of God, what they say should always line up with the Word of God.  If it doesn&#8217;t, then it is the Bible that is always right.  The Apostle Paul commended the Bereans for searching the Scriptures to make sure what he was saying was true.  The Scriptures also tell us to test the spirits.</p>
